data.description:
LOWEST PRICED, TRUE 4 BEDROOM BY OVER 100K IN ALL OF WESTLAKE. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home with a 2-car garage is situated on one of the largest fenced lots within Sky Cove. The master bedroom is conveniently located downstairs, while the upper floor features three bedrooms and a cozy loft. Main living areas boast tile flooring, while the kitchen stands out with its upgraded cabinets and countertops. An oversized, undermount sink, pull-out shelves in the pantry, and a functional kitchen island add to the allure. The master suite impresses with a beautiful shower, upgraded cabinets, quartz counters, and a generously sized closet. This well-maintained home boasts carpeted floors upstairs and features impact windows throughout. Additionally, the property includes a whole house water treatment system for added convenience and quality living. The entire home interior has been freshly painted, providing a refreshed and inviting ambiance. Noteworthy upgrades also include a laundry room with a utility sink, a wood stairwell railing, an upgraded refrigerator, recessed lighting, and an automatic water hose retrieval system for both outside faucets, ensuring ease and convenience in maintaining the outdoor spaces.

Step outside to the covered, screened patio and enjoy the spacious, fenced backyard, uniquely shaped like a pie. Revel in the breathtaking Westlake sunsets from the comfort of your own yard.

Sky Cove, part of the Westlake community, is family-oriented and offers fantastic amenities, including a private gym and a half-court basketball. Residents of Sky Cove enjoy access to Adventure Park which includes a lagoon-style pool with a thrilling 3-story slide, a splash pad, cabanas, and diverse spaces for recreational activities. The community also provides an outdoor concert pavilion, basketball courts, an adult pool, playground, dog park, and a specialized pump park catering to BMX enthusiasts.
